{"tid":1292905,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"身在第三世界國家的故事","createTime":"2019-07-07T13:46:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T16:33:42.000Z","uid":150979,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"60ef4fd8cc99d0fd8211e066f87526805a184306","tid":1292905,"uid":150979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T13:46:27.000Z","msg":"一個禮拜前，開始係非英語、穆斯林國家做義工， 個mentor 有兩個mentee (我同另一個大6 妹)。 個mentor 只係take care 個女。 第一日，我要求mentor 幫我買sim card ，搵籃球場，佢答完okay 就無左件事 (唔只一次)。 點解一定要佢買? 因為當地買sim card 用實名制，需要居民id,  張card 係要申請call 車app account (呢度係極少公共交通工具，地鐵涵蓋既旅遊景點極少)。 <br />\n<br />\n每日工作5小時，咁呢5日，放工就on99 咁 hea 係間宿舍，或者走去對面個shopping mall (語言不通，廢時亂走)，基本上半個mall 既野都食曬，total 食左14餐。 我覺得個mentor 完全係廢，佢唔願意幫我做佢能力範圍內，而我唔能夠做既野 (買sim card)。 呢一刻，我只有少少不愉快。<br />\n<br />\n直到今晚，咩地方都無得去既我，太無聊之下就搵左大6妹WhatsApp 吹水(非溝女，人在異鄉，真係太無聊，傾下今日玩左咩黎)。 佢就話mentor 帶左佢出去玩同食野，轉頭去飲酒，問我黎唔黎?   諗諗下，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">成件事真係好撚鬼</span></span><br />\n<br />\n醒起第3晚，個mentor 問我夜晚食唔食飯，佢地係對面個mall。 我緊係開心，可以一齊食下飯傾計，無咁homesickness 。我當時仲覺得mentor 幾 nice。 事後得知，本身mentor 無諗住叫我，只係想單獨同大6妹食。 <br />\n<br />\n第5日，一大班人gathering,  mentor 又係度flirt 條大6 妹，<span style=\"color: red;\">捉手，摸人，睇人電話</span>。 臨走戈陣，佢幫我call 司機，我話要唱一唱錢先，上網睇呢度d 司機多數唔找錢，佢趕時間 (因為mentor 要單獨送條女番去)，然後話唔洗唱，司機一定找比我。 到左門口，雞同鴨講，司機直接收左我d 錢，唔肯找比我，走左去。<br />\n<br />\n我<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母</span></span>，身為一個mentor, 不公平對待自己既buddy ，我就連續7日，一條友係同一條街行，自己就帶另一個人周圍玩。 知唔知我幾撚悶，身邊一個華人都無，又無咩人識講英文，身在異地，只可以上連登，睇youtube 。 真係好嬲!！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZnE8HPo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZnE8HPo.jpg&h=980aadbc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7eeTTWS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7eeTTWS.jpg&h=8d8a78f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>頭兩日，唔敢出去，都係食呢d</strong></ins>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KQS2Nhi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKQS2Nhi.jpg&h=1cac432e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>條馬路，係無紅綠燈，佢係無提過我有咩tips過馬路，例如 遞手</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qUaS9ww.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqUaS9ww.jpg&h=c26166ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>平時條路就係塞到咁，唔call 車無可能截到車<br />\n</ins></strong>"},{"pid":"484350408f8d3b673146c4086502a64f750f3c2c","tid":1292905,"uid":46282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:01:31.000Z","msg":"係度講有咩用 唔去投訴? 咩組織?邊個國家"},{"pid":"b06e59922a7dc07182c7bff730ab3ae9ba399143","tid":1292905,"uid":150979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"484350408f8d3b673146c4086502a64f750f3c2c","tid":1292905,"uid":46282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:01:31.000Z","msg":"係度講有咩用 唔去投訴? 咩組織?邊個國家"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:44:41.000Z","msg":"身在異地，唔敢亂黎"},{"pid":"4814a125a24f16fd8138da60d7b582719dc93fc2","tid":1292905,"uid":46282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b06e59922a7dc07182c7bff730ab3ae9ba399143","tid":1292905,"uid":150979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"484350408f8d3b673146c4086502a64f750f3c2c","tid":1292905,"uid":46282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:01:31.000Z","msg":"係度講有咩用 唔去投訴? 咩組織?邊個國家"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:44:41.000Z","msg":"身在異地，唔敢亂黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:51:56.000Z","msg":"唔走得架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4786dfabd8c0ef0680fec177baa20db61d42e7a5","tid":1292905,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:25:29.000Z","msg":"唔知點幫你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唯有支持下"},{"pid":"4767e47fe0d5666a82232be3b4615102ec9ac609","tid":1292905,"uid":25973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b06